            <title><![CDATA[前中超球员据报染疫亡年仅37岁 死因为冠病引发基础病恶化]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>年仅37岁的</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>前中超球员据报因感染冠病，引发了基础性疾病恶化而导致死亡。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>据人民体育微博星期二（</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>12月</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>13日）引述媒体报道，前沈阳金德队球员王若吉因感染新冠引发基础性疾病恶化不幸于</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>12日</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>去世。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>一名媒体人赵震称，王若吉患有的基础性疾病是糖尿病。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
